[Auction "N"]
1H Pass 2D Pass 2H Pass 4H Pass Pass Pass
{How do you start this action? [Bid 1H]
You open 1\H and partner responds 2\D.  What do you rebid? 
Partner's 2 over 1 bid sets up a game force.
You have a good-looking hand, but you need to find a trump suit before showing extra strength, so she bids just 2\H.  You are in a game forcing auction, so partner won't pass you.
Partner now jumps to 4\h.  What do you do now? 

Partner's jump to 4\h is Fast Arrival - showing a minimum game forcing hand.  Even though we have extra values, this won't be enough for slam opposite 13 or so points.}

